subject: Football
lead_paragraph: A woman who obtained a restraining order earlier this year in a domestic violence case against the New England Patriots star Randy Moss wants the case dismissed, court records show. Rachelle Washington, 35, filed papers March 3 with the Broward County (Fla.) Circuit Court clerk’s office requesting that the order be dissolved and the case closed. Moss, 31, denied that he harmed Washington at her Florida home on Jan. 6, or that he prevented her from seeking medical attention.
